==Finnish==
===Noun===

hiisi (genitive ''hiiden'', illative ''hiiteen'')

(mild expletive) devil, demon

Finnish synonyms: [[helvetti]], [[halvattu]], [[hitto]], [[piru]]

===Examples===

*''Painu hiiteen!'' Go to hell!
*parent to a child: ''Varo, ettei kaivohiisi vie sinua!'' Be careful, that the well-demon won't take you!